<F P=102>  OW0902065994 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0700 
GMT 7 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW0902065994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, 7 Feb (XINHUA) -- Decree No. 146 of the 
State Council of the People's Republic of China: 
  The "Regulations of the State Council on Working Hours for 
Staff Members and Workers" were passed at the 15th executive 
meeting of the State Council on 24 January 1994 and are hereby 
promulgated for implementation effective 1 March 1994. 
  [Signed] Premier Li Peng 
  [Dated] 3 February 1994 

