Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Lusaka, February 8 (XINHUA) -- A Chinese company 
today handed over two Y-12 aircrafts to the Defense Ministry of 
Zambia at a ceremony held in an airforce base near Lusaka. 
  The two China-made aircrafts were sold on credit by China 
National Aero-Technology Import and Export Corporation. 
