  In reply, Chinese Ambassador to Zambia Yang Zengye said in 
line with the principles of equality, mutual benefits, stress on 
practical results, diversity in forms and attainment of common 
progress, China will further promote the existing friendly 
relations of close cooperation with Zambia. 
  The two aircrafts flew here on January 25. 

