<H3> <TI>   State Council Holds Spring Festival Celebration </TI></H3>
<H4>   Opened by Jiang Zemin </H4>
<F P=102> OW1002030394 Beijing Central Television Program One Network 
in Mandarin 0159 GMT 10 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW1002030394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing Central Television Program One Network 
in Mandarin 0159 GMT 10 Feb 94 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Jiang Zeming's speech at a get-together for Spring Festival </F>
group greetings in Beijing on 10 February 1994] 
  [Text] [Video shows medium close-up shot of Jiang wearing 
a Mao-type jacket, standing in front of a bank on microphones] 
Comrades and friends: 
  Now we begin the get-together for 1994 Spring Festival group 
greetings. [applause] 
  Today is a traditional festival of the people of our 
country. 
On this joyous day, I would like to wish you a happy new year 
on behalf of the party Central Committee and the State Council. 
[applause] 
  Present at today's get-together for group greetings are more 
than 4,000 people, including leading party and state comrades; 
responsible comrades of central party, government, army, and 
mass organizations; retired comrades who have made contributions 
to the socialist revolution and construction; responsible 
persons of various democratic parties and patriotic personages 
without party affiliation; and representatives of minority 
nationalities; as well as foreign experts assisting our country 
in construction and representatives from Beijing's various 
circles. We have happily got together here to usher in the 
Spring Festival and to spend the joyous holiday. [applause] 
  Now I would like to invite Li Peng, Standing Committee 
member 
of the CPC Central Committee Political Bureau and Premier of the 
State Council, to speak. [video cuts to show the audience 
applauding] 

