<H3> <TI>   Li Ruihuan, Hu Jintao Greet Song Ping, Bo Yibo </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1002022294 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 1155 
GMT 9 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW1002022294 </F>
