<H3> <TI>   Leaders Celebrate Spring Festival in Provinces </TI></H3>
<H4>   Leaders Greet Old Comrades </H4>
<F P=102> OW1102063094 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 1146 
GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>

