<H3> <TI>   Leaders Celebrate Spring Festival in Provinces </TI></H3>
<H4>   Qiao Shi Visits Hainan </H4>
<F P=102> HK1402032494 Haikou Hainan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1100 GMT 11 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK1402032494 </F>
<F P=104>  Haikou Hainan People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Qiao Shi, member of the Standing Committee of 
the CPC Central Committee Political Bureau and chairman of the 
National People's Congress Standing Committee, is currently 
spending the Spring Festival with the cadres and masses in 
