Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with 
Chinese characteristics, the people throughout the country will 
continue to implement all the policies and principles of the 
party Central Committee, and China will make greater progress in 
all trades and undertakings. On the Lunar New Year day, Qiao 
