provincial party Secretary Ruan Chongwu, Qiao Shi went to a 
development zone and a natural preservation zone to express his 
Lunar New Year greetings to the cadres and masses there. [words 
indistinct] He hoped that in the new situation Hainan will make 
greater progress in its work. During his visit to Hainan, Qiao 
Shi also participated in local Spring Festival parties. 

